      <item>
        <title>How to centre an image in HTML</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;How to centre an image may be the most commonly asked question from newbies like me. It is actually very simple, you can either use a div wrapper or simply add a class to the img tag itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;using-the-div-wrapper-and-css&quot;&gt;Using the div wrapper and CSS&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Simply add a div around the img tag:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;div&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;img-wrapper&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;img&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;src=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;/img/test.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;alt=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;test&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then in your CSS file, add the following: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;.img-wrapper&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;text-align&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The div will then treat the image as text and align it to the centre. You can align image to the right using the same principle.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;example&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;img-wrapper&quot;&gt;
	&lt;img src=&quot;http://img2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100218161535/streetfighter/images/0/03/Dudley3sportrait.gif&quot; alt=&quot;test&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;adding-a-class-to-the-img-tag-itself&quot;&gt;Adding a class to the img tag itself&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This may be simpler, all you have to do is add a class to your image like the following example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;img&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;src=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;/img/test.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;alt=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;test&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.img-centre&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then in your CSS file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;.img-centre&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;margin-left&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;margin-right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;example-1&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100218161535/streetfighter/images/0/03/Dudley3sportrait.gif&quot; alt=&quot;test&quot; class=&quot;img-centre&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This may be a better option as you can reuse the same class on every image you want to centre instead of adding a div wrapper around each image.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        <pubDate>Mon, 26 May 2014 00:49:00 +0100</pubDate>
        <link>http://colloque.me/tips/2014/05/26/how-to-centre-an-image-in-html/</link>
        <guid isPermaLink="true">http://colloque.me/tips/2014/05/26/how-to-centre-an-image-in-html/</guid>
      </item>
    
      <item>
        <title>How to generate three line menu icon</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;A slide menu or drawer is very common amongst mobilised websites, the most commonly used one must be the 3 parallel lines. I know 3 different ways to generate one:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;using-html-entity&quot;&gt;Using HTML entity&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Turns out there is a handy little HTML entity for that!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ni&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;#9776;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;using-svg&quot;&gt;Using SVG&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to Wikipedia, Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) is an XML-based vector image format for two-dimensional graphics that has support for interactivity and animation.
Just paste the following code into your HTML file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;id=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;YOUR_ID&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;href=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;#YOUR_ACTION&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;svg&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;version=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;1.1&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;xmlns=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;xmlns:xlink=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;x=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;0px&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;y=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;0px&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;viewBox=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;0 0 18 15&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;enable-background=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;new 0 0 18 15&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;xml:space=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;preserve&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;path&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;fill=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;#fff&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;d=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;M18,1.484c0,0.82-0.665,1.484-1.484,1.484H1.484C0.665,2.969,0,2.304,0,1.484l0,0C0,0.665,0.665,0,1.484,0h15.031C17.335,0,18,0.665,18,1.484L18,1.484z&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;path&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;fill=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;#fff&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;d=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;M18,7.516C18,8.335,17.335,9,16.516,9H1.484C0.665,9,0,8.335,0,7.516l0,0c0-0.82,0.665-1.484,1.484-1.484h15.031C17.335,6.031,18,6.696,18,7.516L18,7.516z&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;path&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;fill=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;#fff&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;d=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;M18,13.516C18,14.335,17.335,15,16.516,15H1.484C0.665,15,0,14.335,0,13.516l0,0c0-0.82,0.665-1.484,1.484-1.484h15.031C17.335,12.031,18,12.696,18,13.516L18,13.516z&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then give it a height and width:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;#YOUR_ID&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;height&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;16px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;width&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;18px&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;simply-using-a-png-image&quot;&gt;Simply using a PNG image&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can google that yourself.
Nah, &lt;a href=&quot;http://lmgtfy.com/?q=menu+icon+png&quot;&gt;I will help you out&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;update&quot;&gt;Update&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Just found out about &lt;a href=&quot;http://fontawesome.io&quot;&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/a&gt;, have a look at their amazing work! You can implement Font Awesom’s CSS by adding this single line in the head section:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;link&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;href&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;rel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;stylesheet&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can then add over 400 icons using the &lt;i&gt; tag like this:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;na&quot;&gt;class=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;fa fa-bars&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/i&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; Menu&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;which result in:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-bars&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Menu&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can then style the icon like text, how convenient! Head to &lt;a href=&quot;http://fontawesome.io&quot;&gt;Font Awesome&lt;/a&gt; for more options and example!&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
        <pubDate>Sun, 25 May 2014 11:38:00 +0100</pubDate>
